casebody.data:
Waller M. Adams, Plaintiff, v. Clare M. Torrey et al., Defendants, and T. & G. Assets Realization Corporation, Appellant. Walter M. Goldsmith et al., Respondents.

Reported below, 263 App. Div. 6.

Submitted October 5, 1942; decided October 15, 1942. Osmond K. Fraenkel for motion. William Biel and Chauncey E. Treadwill opposed.

Motion denied with ten dollars costs.
